==English==
===Etymology===
From Hispano-Arabic [[الزوق|الزُوقْ]], from Arabic [[ال]]  .[[زَاوُوقْ|زاووق]] +

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /'azəʊθ/

===Noun===
#''(Alchemy)'' The first principle of [[metal]]s, ''i.e.'', [[mercury]], which was formerly supposed to exist in all metals, and to be extractable from them.
#The universal [[remedy]] of [[Paracelsus]].

